{
  "id": "adv_bond_rei_01_05",
  "title": "一ノ瀬怜5",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei001.m4a",
      "text": "えっと、今日の仕事は……午後の撮影だけね\n久しぶりにゆっくり自主練出来るわ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Hmm‚ today's schedule is… only the afternoon shoot.\nI can finally focus on my personal practice after a long time.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 0.8,
      "sfxList": [
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_phone-tap-02.m4a",
          "delay": 2599.9999999999995
        },
        {
          "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-01.m4a",
          "delay": 10464.693915
        }
      ]
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei002.m4a",
      "text": "……あ、franさん。お疲れ様です\nfranさんも自主練ですか？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Oh‚ fran-san. Good work today.\nAre you also here for personal practice?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 12.4113617579,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-kor001.m4a",
      "text": "しないわよ。この後、事務所で取材だから\nストレッチでもして暇つぶし",
      "translations": {
        "en": "No. I have an interview at the office later.\nI'm just killing time with some stretching.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 18.8495930035,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei003.m4a",
      "text": "（franさんと二人っきり……あまり話したことが）\n（ないから、ちょっと気まずいわ……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（Alone with fran-san… we haven't really talked much‚）\n（so it feels a bit awkward…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 25.6162596702,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei004.m4a",
      "text": "（……それにしても、スタイルが凄くいいわね）\n（開脚している様子も様になっているわ）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（…That being said‚ her physique is incredible.）\n（Even the way she does her leg splits is so graceful.）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 33.0054434458,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei005.m4a",
      "text": "（あの長い手足を惜しみなく使ったダンスは）\n（いつも圧巻よね……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（The way she dances‚ using those long limbs to the fullest‚）\n（is always a masterpiece to behold…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 42.1841512997,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei006.m4a",
      "text": "（ダンスのことについて聞いてみたいけど……）\n（今話しかけたら怒られるかしら……）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I want to ask her about her dancing‚ but…）\n（would she get mad if I spoke to her now?…）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 47.9542645454,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-kor002.m4a",
      "text": "……ちょっと。何ジロジロ見てんのよ\n何か文句でもあるの？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Hey. What are you glancing at?\nDo you have some kind of problem with me?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 55.2741953532,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei007.m4a",
      "text": "す、すみません！　その……franさんの\nスタイルがあまりにもいいから、つい……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "I-I'm sorry! It's just that… fran-san‚\nyour physique is so wonderful that I looked without thinking…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 60.6408620198,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-kor003.m4a",
      "text": "ああ、そういうこと……ふふん、当たり前でしょ？\n私を誰だと思ってるのよ。普通なら見物料取るくらいよ",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Ah‚ so that’s it… Hmph‚ well obviously‚ right?\nWho do you think I am? Normally‚ I'd charge you a viewing fee.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 67.7439458847,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei008.m4a",
      "text": "ええっ、見物料……！？\nちなみに、いくらですか……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What‚ a viewing fee…!?\nJust out of curiosity‚ how much would that be…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 78.9439418157,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-kor004.m4a",
      "text": "そうね……\nパリコレを経験したトップモデルの私なら……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Let's see…\nFor a top model like me who's walked the Paris Collection…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 84.4506087304,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei009.m4a",
      "text": "（余計なこと聞かなきゃ良かった……）\n（これってカツアゲってやつじゃないの？）",
      "translations": {
        "en": "（I shouldn't have asked that…）\n（Doesn't this feel a bit like being shakedown?）",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 90.4172753971,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-kor005.m4a",
      "text": "同じ事務所のよしみで、三百円ってところね",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Since we're in the same agency‚ let’s say 300 yen.",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 97.4818785032,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei010.m4a",
      "text": "……え？　……三百円？　意外とお安いんですね……？",
      "translations": {
        "en": "…Eh? …300 yen? That's surprisingly cheap…?",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 101.6485451699,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-kor006.m4a",
      "text": "何よ、馬鹿にしてるの！？　三百円を馬鹿にすると\n三百円に泣くのよ！　じゃあ五百円払いなさいよ！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "What‚ are you mocking me?! If you underestimate 300 yen‚\nyou'll end up crying over 300 yen! Fine‚ pay 500 yen then!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 108.1456433933,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei011.m4a",
      "text": "五百円！？　は、はい。それなら私でも……",
      "translations": {
        "en": "500 yen!? O-Oh‚ I see. If it's that much‚ even I can…",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 116.5789813043,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "kor",
      "speakerName": "fran",
      "speakerNameEn": "fran",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-fran.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-kor007.m4a",
      "text": "は？　何、あんた達そんなにもらってんの！？\nちょっと、給料教えなさい！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "Huh? What‚ do you guys get paid that much?!\nHey‚ tell me your salary!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 120.7480732601,
      "sfxList": []
    },
    {
      "type": "dialogue",
      "speakerCode": "rei",
      "speakerName": "一ノ瀬怜",
      "speakerNameEn": "Rei",
      "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-rei.png",
      "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/bondStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05/sud_vo_adv_bond_rei_01_05-rei012.m4a",
      "text": "え、ええっ……！　さすがにそれは……！\nお給料は個人情報です！",
      "translations": {
        "en": "W-Wait…! That's a bit too much…!\nSalary is personal information!",
        "id": ""
      },
      "startTime": 127.3480768205,
      "sfxList": []
    }
  ]
}